                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300218-95-off524 t18300218-95-crimeloc527"></join>. The prisoner was a <rs id="t18300218-95-deflabel528" type="occupation">journeyman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300218-95-defend644 t18300218-95-deflabel528"></join> in his shop for three or four months, but did not live in the house; we missed a coat of a customers on the 9th of February - we did not know where the prisoner lodged till he told us in the evening; we went there with an officer, and found five gilt buttons, but the coat we found in pawn.</p>
               <p>
            
